nlc config - Manage configuration

[1mUsage:[0m
  nlc config COMMAND
  nlc config [COMMAND] --help | -h

[1mCommands:[0m
  [32mshow[0m     Show confiruation and environment
  [32mclear[0m    Delete the config file (falling back to default values)
  [32medit[0m     Edit the confiruation file (create it first if needed)
  [32mcreate[0m   Create a new config file
